    "## Limitations\n",
    "\n",
    "This screening model is intentionally stylized. It does not represent:\n",
    "- full AC/DC power flow\n",
    "- line loading, voltage stability, or dispatch\n",
    "- probabilistic component fragility\n",
    "- restoration dynamics\n",
    "- historical infrastructure build-out by event year\n",
    "- direct empirical validation against observed blackout records\n",
    "\n",
    "In **v5r**, service adequacy is a proxy based on installed generation capacity relative to a bus-attached population proxy, normalized against the intact system baseline. This is a screening construct, not a full supply-demand adequacy model.\n"
